oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Woldridge's Rexall Drugs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Woldridge's Rexall Drugs. There are signs for Kodak and Swift's Ice Cream. There is also a sign shaped like a chicken that advertises a "Chickburger Sandwich."
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Signs (Notices); Drugstores; Stores & shops; Window displays; Chickens
